    "sections": [
      {
        "title": "Promotion",
        "description": "The new APS-C sensor is designed to provide additional telephoto effect by increasing the focal length by approximately 1.6x while retaining its resolution of 32.5-megapixels, allowing even more creative freedom for post-processing."
      },
      {
        "title": "Promotion",
        "description": ""
      },
      {
        "title": "Promotion",
        "description": ""
      },
      {
        "title": "Key Features",
        "description": ""
      },
      {
        "title": "Superior Image Quality",
        "description": ""
      },
      {
        "title": "High Resolution",
        "description": "The EOS R7 is equipped with a new approximately 32.5-megapixel APS-C CMOS sensor combined with DIGIC X image processor, allowing for high-speed readout and high image quality."
      },
      {
        "title": "High Speed, High Precision",
        "description": ""
      },
      {
        "title": "Up to 30 FPS High-speed Continuous Shooting",
        "description": "Perform high-speed continuous shooting at up to 15 fps with the mechanical shutter with AF/AE tracking, almost on par with the EOS-1D X Mark III’s capability."
      },
      {
        "title": "Intelligent Tracking and Recognition",
        "description": "Accurately tracks what matters most. The EOS R7 inherits EOS R3's ability to differentiate elements within the frame and determine which subject to track."
      },
      {
        "title": "People Priority",
        "description": "Based on unique detection algorithms, the EOS R7's Eye Detection AF detects people even with masks on. When its Head Detection AF is activated, the EOS R7 has the capability of detecting people wearing goggles."
      },
      {
        "title": "Movie Making",
        "description": ""
      },
      {
        "title": "HDR PQ Movies",
        "description": "Record 4:2:2 10-bit HDR PQ movies with higher brightness, wider tonal range and wider colour gamut for playback on HDR-compatible screens."
      },
      {
        "title": "Convenient Features",
        "description": ""
      },
      {
        "title": "Built Solid",
        "description": ""
      },
      {
        "title": "EVF",
        "description": "The EOS R7 features a new electronic viewfinder (EVF) developed by Canon."
      },
      {
        "title": "Reliable Shutter",
        "description": "The EOS R7 is equipped with a durable shutter capable of shooting up to 200,000 cycles and is designed to support better image stabilisation."
      },
      {
        "title": "Connections",
        "description": ""
      },
      {
        "title": "Wi-Fi",
        "description": "Transfer files wirelessly and quickly from the EOS R7 to your smart device or PC using high-speed 2.4 GHz built-in Wi-Fi*. The EOS R7 supports Wi-Fi Protected Access 3 (WPA3) for added file security on wireless networks.*"
      },
      {
        "title": "Multi-Function Shoe",
        "description": "Sporting a next-generation interface with dust- and water-resistant design, the brand-new Multi-Function Shoe supports various types of audio and video accessories without the need of attaching cables."
      },
      {
        "title": "Multi-Function Shoe",
        "description": ""
      },
      {
        "title": "For Flash Photography",
        "description": "Enjoy the convenience and ease of wireless flash photography and a cleaner setup with this radio-enabled and battery-less Speedlite transmitter that can remotely control multiple Speedlite units."
      },
